---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Blackout — a multi-sport movement for diversity and inclusivity, starting with pickleball and expanding across sports.">

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-muted font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Story</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight">Diversity in Every Sport.</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Blackout is a movement — built on the belief that every sport should reflect the diversity of the people who play it. We started with pickleball, the fastest-growing sport in America, because we saw an opportunity to change the face of the game.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6">
          Our mission is to celebrate diversity and inclusivity within sports. We're dedicated to increasing Black representation in communities that have historically lacked it — while welcoming everyone, regardless of background, to join us in playing, supporting, and sharing the games we love.
        </p>

        <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6">
          But Blackout doesn't stop at pickleball. We're building a multi-sport brand that carries this energy to tennis, and beyond. Wherever there's a court, a field, or a game — Blackout will be there, bringing bold representation and community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Vision Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 border border-gray-100">
        <p class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Vision</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">Bigger Than One Sport</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          Blackout is the parent brand — an umbrella for every sport vertical we launch. Blackout Pickleball is where it all started. Blackout Tennis is coming next. And as the movement grows, so does our reach. Each sport gets its own community, its own gear, and its own identity — united under the Blackout name.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-accent/10 text-accent-dark font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">🏓 Pickleball — Active</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">🎾 Tennis — Coming Soon</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 font-semibold rounded-full text-sm">🏅 More Sports — Coming Soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder Section -->
      <div class="mt-8 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 bg-surface-warm">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4 font-display">Meet the Founder</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          Jonathan Dapaah founded Blackout with a bold vision: to create vibrant, inclusive spaces across sports. A passionate athlete himself, Jonathan saw that many sports communities didn't reflect the diversity of the world around them — and he set out to change that. Starting with pickleball, he built a brand that celebrates Black representation while welcoming everyone to the court.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Gear Section -->
      <div class="mt-8 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 border border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4">Performance Gear</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
          Our high-performance gear is crafted from a premium 85% Polyester and 15% Spandex blend. Designed to release heat and wick moisture, our breathable 4-way stretch fabric ensures perfect shape recovery and extreme freedom of movement. Whether you're on the court for a casual game or competing at the highest level, Blackout gear performs.
        </p>
        <a href="/shop" class="inline-flex items-center mt-6 text-accent hover:text-accent-dark font-semibold transition-colors gap-2 group">
          Shop the Collection
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
